      "range": "972-1006",
      "markText": "穿过长长的县界隧道，就是雪国。夜的底色变成银白。火车在信号所停下了。",
      "totalCount": 1800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=972&rangeEnd=1006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=972&rangeEnd=1006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_8_28553-28592",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "28553-28592",
      "markText": "岛村勉强稳住脚跟，抬头望去。就在那一刻，银河仿佛哗啦一声，朝他的心房倾泻下来。",
      "totalCount": 1570,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=28553&rangeEnd=28592",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=28553&rangeEnd=28592"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_5_6705-6740",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6705-6740",
      "markText": "岛村不喜欢女人这样敏锐。她不该变得这么犀利，不管是为他，还是为她自己。",
      "totalCount": 1215,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6705&rangeEnd=6740",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6705&rangeEnd=6740"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_6_2742-2797",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2742-2797",
      "markText": "驹子这种活法，岛村认为它徒劳无益，又悲叹它是渺茫的期盼。但这对她自己的确是有价值的，也充溢在那铿锵的琴音之中。",
      "totalCount": 1184,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2742&rangeEnd=2797",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2742&rangeEnd=2797"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_6_8839-8857",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8839-8857",
      "markText": "岛村突然对驹子生出一种生理上的厌恶。",
      "totalCount": 1056,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8839&rangeEnd=8857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8839&rangeEnd=8857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_6245-6344",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6245-6344",
      "markText": "不曾亲眼看到的舞蹈，好比天方夜谭，是镜花水月，是天国之诗。美其名曰研究，不过是天马行空的想象。他品评的不是舞蹈家们肢体演绎出的灵动舞姿，而是他通过西文和图片想象出的幻影，就像憧憬不曾见过的爱情一样。",
      "totalCount": 1022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6245&rangeEnd=6344",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6245&rangeEnd=6344"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_8_27849-27890",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "27849-27890",
      "markText": "不知为何，岛村没有感到死亡，只是觉得在叶子体内，生命在改变形状，而那一刻就是分界。",
      "totalCount": 1003,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=27849&rangeEnd=27890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=27849&rangeEnd=27890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_8_7080-7158",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7080-7158",
      "markText": "岛村感到某种奇妙的魅力，可不知为什么，内心反而燃起了对驹子炽热的爱。私奔似的带个来历不明的姑娘回东京—用这种激烈的方式向驹子谢罪，或者，也可以说是一种刑罚。",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7080&rangeEnd=7158",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7080&rangeEnd=7158"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_5710-5732",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5710-5732",
      "markText": "想同她做朋友是真，内心却也越过了友谊的浅滩。",
      "totalCount": 858,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5710&rangeEnd=5732",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5710&rangeEnd=5732"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_5_11287-11367",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11287-11367",
      "markText": "在温泉旅馆听按摩女谈论艺伎的身世，是再寻常不过的事。但岛村未曾料想到驹子为了未婚夫出来做艺伎，这故事太老套，他总觉得难以置信。也许是因为这与他的道德观念相抵触。",
      "totalCount": 798,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11287&rangeEnd=11367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11287&rangeEnd=11367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_4905-4981",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4905-4981",
      "markText": "“要是有了那种关系，也许我明天就不想再见你，也提不起劲头跟你聊天了。我从山上来到村子里，难得碰到个能说上话的人，所以我不招惹你。说到底，我只是个过客。”",
      "totalCount": 754,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4905&rangeEnd=4981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4905&rangeEnd=4981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_5051-5104",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5051-5104",
      "markText": "再说，要是我找个你不喜欢的女人，以后我们再见面，你也会感到厌恶。还不如你帮我选一个，这样你心里也好受些吧？",
      "totalCount": 750,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5051&rangeEnd=5104",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5051&rangeEnd=5104"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_6_6028-6092",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6028-6092",
      "markText": "所谓难过，是对一个过客陷得太深的担忧，还是极力压抑自己而产生的痛楚？莫非她用情至深，已到了这种地步？岛村思忖着，沉默了好一阵子。",
      "totalCount": 700,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6028&rangeEnd=6092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6028&rangeEnd=6092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_3137-3187",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3137-3187",
      "markText": "女子看上去出奇地洁净，仿佛连脚趾窝都是干净的。岛村不禁怀疑，这也许是因为自己的眼睛刚看过初夏的群山。",
      "totalCount": 686,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3137&rangeEnd=3187",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3137&rangeEnd=3187"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_8_6697-6714",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6697-6714",
      "markText": "“那我回去的时候，带你一起走吧？”",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6697&rangeEnd=6714",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6697&rangeEnd=6714"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_8_17160-17247",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "17160-17247",
      "markText": "然而，这种爱意所能留下的痕迹，恐怕都不及一块绉纱。纵令衣料在工艺品中寿命最短，但只要好好爱惜，五十年前乃至更早的绉纱，穿在身上仍不会褪色。而人的相依相伴，却未必能长久过绉纱。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17160&rangeEnd=17247",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17160&rangeEnd=17247"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_5551-5606",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5551-5606",
      "markText": "要满足对女人的欲望，岛村有更简单而无负罪感的办法，不用打她的主意。她太过洁净，初见她时，岛村就对她另眼相待了。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5551&rangeEnd=5606",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5551&rangeEnd=5606"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047367_4_5308-5363",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5308-5363",
      "markText": "他们说，分开之后，那些有点喜欢却又没说破的，才总叫人惦念，一直也忘不了。对方还能想起你，写封信来，也是因为这样",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5308&rangeEnd=5363",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04932050813ab7900g0179b5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5308&rangeEnd=5363"
    },
    {
